<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<title>Happy Birthday 🎉🌙</title>
<style>
  body {
    font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    text-align: center;
    background: #fff8e1;
    color: #333;
    padding: 50px;
  }
  h1 {
    color: #ff6f61;
    animation: glow 1s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
  }
  p {
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  button {
    padding: 10px 20px;
    font-size: 16px;
    margin-top: 20px;
    cursor: pointer;
    background: #ffca28;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
  }
  @keyframes glow {
    0% { text-shadow: 0 0 5px #ff6f61; }
    100% { text-shadow: 0 0 20px #ff6f61; }
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
  <h1>Happy Birthday & Selamat Lebaran! 🎉🌙</h1>
  <p>I hope you get everything you’ve been wishing for, and semoga selalu dikelilingi hal-hal dan orang-orang baik.</p>
  <p>Di umur baru ini, semoga makin bahagia, makin dewasa, menemukan jati diri kamu, dan hari-harimu selalu sehangat momen Lebaran ini 🌙✨</p>
  
  <button onclick="showSurprise()">Click for a surprise 😏</button>

  <p id="surprise" style="display:none; margin-top:20px; color:#ff4081; font-weight:bold;"></p>

  <script>
    function showSurprise() {
      document.getElementById('surprise').style.display = 'block';
      document.getElementById('surprise').innerText = "Pssst… someone here really cares about you 😌🎂";
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
